title: Carson Trends 8/29: Keanu Reeves, Breitbart, Dark Brandon, Serena Williams, MTV VMA

description:
In this edition of Carson Trends, Jack and Miles discuss Keanu Reeves showing up at a random wedding, the new Breitbart movie 'My Son Hunter', the confusing "Dark Brandon" meme, Serena Williams' final US Open, and the madness that was the MTV VMAs!
